"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Iran accuses the US of breaking the truce, saying it attacked an oil tanker and coastal areas. However, US President Donald Trump insists the ceasefire with Tehran is still ongoing. Both sides report responding to many drone attacks shortly after the truce began, which was meant to celebrate the Soviet Union's victory over Nazi Germany.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran Accuses US of Breaking Truce\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ir\u00e1n dice que Estados Unidos rompi\u00f3 la tregua atacando un barco de petr\u00f3leo y \u00e1reas costeras. Pero el presidente de Estados Unidos, Donald Trump, dice que la tregua con Teher\u00e1n sigue. Ambos lados dicen que respondieron a muchos ataques de drones poco despu\u00e9s de que la tregua comenzara, que era para celebrar la victoria de la Uni\u00f3n Sovi\u00e9tica sobre la Alemania nazi.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ir\u00e1n acusa a EE.UU. de romper tregua\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Constitutional Court has stated that Members of Parliament were wrong to stop impeachment proceedings against Cyril Ramaphosa.\",            \"english_title\": \"Court on Ramaphosa Impeachment\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Tribunal Constitucional dijo que los miembros del parlamento estaban equivocados al detener el proceso de destituci\u00f3n contra Cyril Ramaphosa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tribunal sobre destituci\u00f3n de Ramaphosa\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Officials had warned against climbing the active volcano due to safety concerns.\",            \"english_title\": \"Volcano Climbing Warning\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los oficiales advirtieron no subir al volc\u00e1n activo por preocupaciones de seguridad.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Advertencia de subir volc\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"An international air body suggests that accepting US-grade jet fuel more widely could prevent supply issues.\",            \"english_title\": \"Jet Fuel Supply Suggestion\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un grupo internacional de aviaci\u00f3n sugiere que aceptar m\u00e1s el combustible de avi\u00f3n de grado estadounidense podr\u00eda prevenir problemas de suministro.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Sugerencia sobre combustible de avi\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Japan is seeing its largest anti-war protests in decades, showing a population divided over changes to its pacifist constitution.\",            \"english_title\": \"Japan Anti-War Protests\",            \"translated_version\": \"Jap\u00f3n est\u00e1 viendo sus mayores protestas contra la guerra en d\u00e9cadas, mostrando una poblaci\u00f3n dividida sobre cambios en su constituci\u00f3n pacifista.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Protestas contra la guerra en Jap\u00f3n\"        }    ]}"